my father, Erhard,

38:26.208 --> 38:29.333
moved us here after the Second World War.

38:29.916 --> 38:32.458
Er, why? Ah, you may ask.

38:33.250 --> 38:36.291
My, uh, my father taught me the...

38:37.000 --> 38:40.125
the value of, uh, privacy
from an early age.

38:41.375 --> 38:44.083
I was... I was a good student.

38:44.166 --> 38:47.750
