learning you've been banging my roommate?

49:01.541 --> 49:04.458
Her whole life, I bet.
It's like a dream come true.

49:05.916 --> 49:08.166
-I'll meet her at the airport.
-Okay, stop.

49:09.250 --> 49:10.500
Not another word.

49:20.125 --> 49:22.791
