49:36.583 --> 49:38.708
or in Paris,
or wherever you want it to be.

49:38.791 --> 49:42.458
Your life, your whole world up
until this moment,

49:42.708 --> 49:44.375
was more or less perfect.

49:45.291 --> 49:47.458
Except for the time
we had to put down your horse

49:47.541 --> 49:49.375
when it fell jumping over a steeple.

49:51.458 --> 49:53.000
