to go to the party

50:16.833 --> 50:18.875
and not tell your mother about Astrid?

50:18.958 --> 50:20.166
You're kidding.

50:20.333 --> 50:22.583
-Am I? How much?

50:23.500 --> 50:25.791
You go to the party,
you don't tell your mother,

50:25.875 --> 50:27.208
and I continue to see Astrid.

50:27.291 --> 50:30.000
-I'm getting her an apartment in New York.

50:30.083 --> 50:31.750
-This is so fucked up.
-No.

50:31.833 --> 50:33.458
This is how problems are solved.

50:33.833 --> 50:36.916
What's fucked up
is your inability to see that.

50:37.750 --> 50:38.750
How much?

50:42.625 --> 50:43.833
I wanna talk to a lawyer.

50:44.208 --> 50:47.666
Great. Mine's on his way over now.
We can both talk to him.

50:49.375 --> 50:52.666
First of all, congratulations, Simone.
Graduation.

50:52.750 --> 50:53.958
Fuck you, Jeff.

