51:22.208 --> 51:24.208
-Does that make sense to you?

51:26.833 --> 51:27.666
Hm.

51:27.750 --> 51:29.208
Mum's plane's gonna be early.

51:30.208 --> 51:32.833
Maybe I should go and get her
and we can discuss this all together

51:32.916 --> 51:34.791
