53:43.416 --> 53:44.250
No.

53:44.708 --> 53:45.708
She's in her room.

53:46.625 --> 53:48.750
A little anxious about the day's events.

53:49.208 --> 53:52.000
I prefer the other one better.
The Versace.

53:52.375 --> 53:53.791
It brings out your eyes.

53:53.875 --> 53:55.750
